            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/39834124/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/39834124/" class="">全文</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/tu574074469/" class=" " title="我是徐菇凉">我是徐菇凉</a>
                (在紙疊的世界里有一座我們的花園)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
